---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import TopBar from "../components/TopBar.astro";
import LGUFooter from "../components/LGUFooter.astro";
---
<Layout title="About | Build Watch LGU" description="Learn about Build Watch, the Santa Cruz LGU Project Monitoring and Evaluation System.">
  <TopBar />
  <main class="flex flex-col items-center w-full px-4 pt-36 pb-12 min-h-[60vh] relative about-bg fade-in-about">
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="mb-20 w-full flex flex-col items-center">
        <span class="text-[#EB3C3C] font-bold text-lg mb-2 block self-start ml-2">About Us</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#7A1F1F] mb-2 self-start ml-2">What is Build Watch?</h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#FE5353] rounded-full mb-6 self-start ml-2"></div>
        <div class="w-full">
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[#222] mb-4">BUILD WATCH is an official web-based Project Monitoring and Evaluation System developed specifically for the Municipality of Santa Cruz, Laguna to improve the transparency, efficiency, and accountability of local governance.</p>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[#222] mb-4">Designed to monitor both infrastructure projects—such as the construction of the Santa Cruz Barangay Health Center—and social development programs like the 4Ps (Pantawid Pamilyang Pilipino Program) and Social Pension, BUILD WATCH allows real-time tracking of project progress and performance.</p>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[#222] mb-4">The system brings together four key user groups that collaborate within a structured digital workflow:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-8 text-base md:text-lg text-[#222] mb-4">
            <li><b>External Implementing Units (EPIU)</b> carry out the actual implementation of projects and submit progress updates directly to the system.</li>
            <li><b>The Project Monitoring Committee (PMC)</b> reviews, validates, and resolves implementation issues based on submitted data.</li>
            <li><b>LGU Internal Units (LGU-IU)</b> oversee the strategic and administrative aspects, ensuring alignment with local policies and responding to flagged concerns.</li>
            <li><b>External Monitoring Stakeholders (EMS)</b>—such as NGOs and provincial representatives—provide independent assessments and promote transparency by monitoring on behalf of the public.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[#222]">Each group has a clearly defined role, and together, they ensure that every project funded and launched by the LGU is executed with integrity, monitored effectively, and evaluated responsibly.<br/>BUILD WATCH is more than a system—it's a digital commitment to good governance and public trust in Santa Cruz, Laguna.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- Mission & Vision Section -->
      <section class="mb-20 relative flex flex-col items-center w-full">
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 -top-14 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] max-w-full z-20 flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg flex items-center justify-between px-8 py-4">
            <img src="/ph-seal.png" alt="PH Seal" class="w-20 h-20 object-contain" />
            <img src="/build-watch-logo.png" alt="Build Watch Logo" class="w-24 h-24 object-contain" />
            <img src="/santa-cruz-seal.png" alt="Santa Cruz Seal" class="w-20 h-20 object-contain" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-0 w-full mt-20">
          <div class="flex-1 rounded-l-2xl rounded-r-none bg-[#EB3C3C]/90 shadow-lg px-10 py-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition hover:bg-[#EB3C3C] hover:shadow-xl">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-white text-base md:text-lg text-center font-medium">To provide a transparent, efficient, and collaborative digital platform that empowers the LGU, implementers, and stakeholders to monitor, evaluate, and ensure the successful delivery of public projects and programs in Santa Cruz, Laguna.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 rounded-r-2xl rounded-l-none bg-[#EB3C3C]/90 shadow-lg px-10 py-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition hover:bg-[#EB3C3C] hover:shadow-xl">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
            <p class="text-white text-base md:text-lg text-center font-medium">A transparent and accountable local government where every project and program is effectively monitored, digitally connected, and truly felt by the community.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- Features Section -->
      <section class="mb-20 w-full flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg px-10 py-10 w-full">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#333] mb-8 text-center">Build Watch Features</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow border border-[#EB3C3C]/10 transition hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-[#EB3C3C]" tabindex="0">
              <span class="text-[#EB3C3C] text-4xl mb-2"><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-8 h-8' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M3 3v18h18'/><rect x='7' y='13' width='2' height='5' fill='#EB3C3C'/><rect x='11' y='9' width='2' height='9' fill='#EB3C3C'/><rect x='15' y='5' width='2' height='13' fill='#EB3C3C'/></svg></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Real-Time Project Monitoring</h3>
              <p class="text-center text-[#7A1F1F] text-base">Track the physical and financial status of LGU projects and programs as updates are submitted from the field.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow border border-[#EB3C3C]/10 transition hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-[#EB3C3C]" tabindex="0">
              <span class="text-[#EB3C3C] text-4xl mb-2"><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-8 h-8' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M12 4v16m8-8H4'/></svg></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Multi-Role User Access</h3>
              <p class="text-center text-[#7A1F1F] text-base">Custom portals for implementers, LGU offices, monitors, and administrators based on their assigned roles and functions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow border border-[#EB3C3C]/10 transition hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-[#EB3C3C]" tabindex="0">
              <span class="text-[#EB3C3C] text-4xl mb-2"><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-8 h-8' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><rect x='4' y='4' width='16' height='16' rx='2' fill='#EB3C3C' stroke='none'/><rect x='7' y='7' width='10' height='10' rx='1' fill='white' stroke='none'/></svg></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Centralized Project Dashboard</h3>
              <p class="text-center text-[#7A1F1F] text-base">View consolidated data for all ongoing infrastructure and social development projects in one organized dashboard.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow border border-[#EB3C3C]/10 transition hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-[#EB3C3C]" tabindex="0">
              <span class="text-[#EB3C3C] text-4xl mb-2"><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-8 h-8' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M5 13l4 4L19 7'/></svg></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Data Validation & Reporting</h3>
              <p class="text-center text-[#7A1F1F] text-base">Enable monitoring bodies to review submissions, validate reports, and escalate implementation concerns when needed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow border border-[#EB3C3C]/10 transition hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-[#EB3C3C]" tabindex="0">
              <span class="text-[#EB3C3C] text-4xl mb-2"><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-8 h-8' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10' stroke='#EB3C3C' stroke-width='2' fill='none'/><path d='M12 8v4l3 3' stroke='#EB3C3C' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'/></svg></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Transparent Stakeholder Oversight</h3>
              <p class="text-center text-[#7A1F1F] text-base">Allow external stakeholders such as NGOs and provincial monitors to observe project progress and contribute feedback.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow border border-[#EB3C3C]/10 transition hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-[#EB3C3C]" tabindex="0">
              <span class="text-[#EB3C3C] text-4xl mb-2"><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='w-8 h-8' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor'><rect x='6' y='6' width='12' height='12' rx='2' fill='#EB3C3C' stroke='none'/><path d='M9 12l2 2 4-4' stroke='white' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'/></svg></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Secure System Administration</h3>
              <p class="text-center text-[#7A1F1F] text-base">Manage users, roles, and data integrity through a secure backend interface exclusive to system administrators.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- Testimonial Section -->
      <section class="mb-12 flex flex-row gap-8 items-stretch w-full">
        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#EB3C3C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
            </svg>
            <blockquote class="text-[#222] text-lg italic">"The Build Watch system reflects the kind of innovation we need in local governance—transparent, efficient, and people-centered. It sets a strong example of how digital solutions can truly improve project delivery and public trust."</blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#EB3C3C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
            </svg>
            <a href="#" class="text-[#1A4CA3] font-bold hover:underline focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#EB3C3C] rounded">Gov. Elmer V. Dela Peña</a>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[#7A1F1F] text-sm font-semibold ml-8">Department: Provincial Government of Laguna</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition hover:shadow-xl"></div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <LGUFooter />
  <style>
    .about-bg {
      background: url('/about-page-bg.png') center center / cover no-repeat fixed;
    }
    .fade-in-about {
      animation: fadeInAbout 1.1s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
    }
    @keyframes fadeInAbout {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
  </style>
</Layout> 